ğŸ® Hangman Game (Python)

A simple and fun Hangman game built in Python!
The player must guess a hidden word (animal names in this version) before the hangman drawing is completed. Each wrong guess brings the player one step closer to losing!

This project uses:

Random word selection

ASCII art for the hangman

Input validation

Game loop with win/lose detection

âœ¨ Features
ğŸ”¤ Random Word Generator

The game randomly selects a word from a list of animal names stored in wordslist.py.

ğŸ¨ ASCII Hangman Art

The player sees the hangman progressively drawn after each wrong guess.

âœ” Input Validation

Only single alphabet letters allowed

Repeated guesses are blocked

ğŸ† Win/Lose Conditions

Win: all letters are guessed

Lose: 6 wrong guesses (full hangman)

