ğŸ§  How It Works

The game picks a random word.

A hint of underscores (_ _ _) is displayed.

The player guesses letters one by one.

Correct guesses fill in the hint.

Wrong guesses draw more of the hangman.

Game ends when:

The word is fully revealed â†’ You Win

The hangman is complete â†’ You Lose

ğŸ›  Requirements

Python 3.x

No external libraries required

ğŸ“Œ Notes

The word list includes 100+ animal names.

The code uses sets to track guessed letters.

ASCII art is stored in a dictionary for easy modification.

